---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for MakerFriends.com - How we collect, use, and protect your personal data in compliance with GDPR."
>
  <Navigation />

  <main class="flex-1">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section
      class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white"
    >
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100">
          Your privacy is important to us. Learn how we collect, use, and
          protect your personal data.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-blue-200 mt-4">Last updated: January 16, 2025</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>1.1 Newsletter Subscriptions</h3>
        <p>When you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Email Address:</strong> Required for sending newsletters
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Consent Records:</strong> Your explicit consent to receive communications
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Subscription Metadata:</strong> Timestamp, source, and preferences
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Usage Analytics:</strong> Open rates and click-through rates
            (anonymized)
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3>1.2 Website Usage</h3>
        <p>We may collect anonymous usage data including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on site</li>
          <li>Browser type and device information</li>
          <li>General geographic location (country/region level)</li>
          <li>Referral sources</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="data-processing">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>

        <h3>2.1 Newsletter Communications</h3>
        <p>We use your email address to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Send newsletters about MakerSpaces, projects, and community events
          </li>
          <li>Provide updates about MakerFriends platform</li>
          <li>Share relevant maker community content</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.2 Analytics and Improvement</h3>
        <p>We use aggregated, anonymous data to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
          <li>Understand community interests and preferences</li>
          <li>Optimize newsletter content and delivery</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Processing and Storage</h2>

        <h3>3.1 Newsletter Management</h3>
        <p>
          We use <strong>Buttondown</strong> as our newsletter service provider:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Data Location:</strong> Buttondown's secure servers (GDPR compliant)
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Retention:</strong> Until you unsubscribe or request deletion
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Security:</strong> Industry-standard encryption and security
            measures
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3.2 Website Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          We may use analytics services that collect anonymous usage data to
          help us understand how visitors use our website.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>

        <p>As a data subject, you have the following rights:</p>

        <h3>4.1 Right of Access</h3>
        <p>
          You can request information about the personal data we hold about you.
        </p>

        <h3>4.2 Right to Rectification</h3>
        <p>
          You can request correction of inaccurate or incomplete personal data.
        </p>

        <h3>4.3 Right to Erasure</h3>
        <p>
          You can request deletion of your personal data ("right to be
          forgotten").
        </p>

        <h3>4.4 Right to Data Portability</h3>
        <p>
          You can request a copy of your data in a structured, machine-readable
          format.
        </p>

        <h3>4.5 Right to Withdraw Consent</h3>
        <p>
          You can withdraw your consent for newsletter communications at any
          time by:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Clicking the unsubscribe link in any newsletter</li>
          <li>
            Contacting us directly at <a href="mailto:privacy@makerfriends.com"
              >privacy@makerfriends.com</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Data Security</h2>

        <p>
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to
          protect your personal data:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Encryption of data in transit and at rest</li>
          <li>Regular security assessments and updates</li>
          <li>Limited access to personal data on a need-to-know basis</li>
          <li>Secure data processing agreements with third-party providers</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Cookies and Tracking</h2>

        <p>Our website may use cookies for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Essential website functionality</li>
          <li>Analytics and performance monitoring</li>
          <li>Remembering your preferences</li>
        </ul>

        <p>You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.</p>

        <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>

        <h3>7.1 Buttondown</h3>
        <p>
          We use Buttondown for newsletter management. Their privacy policy: <a
            href="https://buttondown.email/privacy"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >
            buttondown.email/privacy
          </a>
        </p>

        <h3>7.2 Cloudflare</h3>
        <p>
          Our website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Their privacy policy: <a
            href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacy/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >
            cloudflare.com/privacy
          </a>
        </p>

        <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>

        <p>
          We retain your personal data only as long as necessary for the
          purposes outlined in this policy:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Newsletter Data:</strong> Until you unsubscribe or request deletion
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Analytics Data:</strong> Aggregated and anonymized data may be
            retained longer
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> Some data may be retained to comply
            with legal obligations
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>9. International Data Transfers</h2>

        <p>
          Your data may be transferred to and processed in countries outside the
          European Economic Area (EEA). We ensure appropriate safeguards are in
          place, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Adequacy decisions by the European Commission</li>
          <li>Standard contractual clauses</li>
          <li>Certification schemes and codes of conduct</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>

        <p>
          Our services are not directed to children under 16. We do not
          knowingly collect personal data from children under 16. If you believe
          we have collected data from a child, please contact us immediately.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>

        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify
          you of any material changes by:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Posting the updated policy on our website</li>
          <li>Sending an email notification to newsletter subscribers</li>
          <li>Updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this policy</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>12. Contact Information</h2>

        <p>
          If you have questions about this privacy policy or wish to exercise
          your rights, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Email:</strong>
            <a href="mailto:privacy@makerfriends.com"
              >privacy@makerfriends.com</a
            >
          </li>
          <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="/contact">Contact Form</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p>We will respond to your inquiry within 30 days.</p>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-400">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">
            Quick Actions
          </h3>
          <ul class="text-blue-800 space-y-2">
            <li>
              • <a href="mailto:privacy@makerfriends.com" class="underline"
                >Request data access or deletion</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              • <a href="/contact" class="underline"
                >Contact us with privacy questions</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              • <a href="mailto:unsubscribe@makerfriends.com" class="underline"
                >Unsubscribe from newsletters</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
